---
// Testimonials.astro - Client testimonials component
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What Our Clients Say</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Don't just take our word for it - hear what our clients have to say about our translation services.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-toast-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-toast-600 font-bold text-xl">
            M
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Maria Rodriguez</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Marketing Director, Global Tech</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
            <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          "The translation quality exceeded our expectations. Our product documentation was translated with perfect technical accuracy while maintaining our brand voice across five languages."
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-toast-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-toast-600 font-bold text-xl">
            J
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">James Chen</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">CEO, E-commerce Solutions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
            <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          "The website localization was seamless and helped us expand into three new markets. Our conversion rates increased by 40% in the first month after launch."
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-toast-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-toast-600 font-bold text-xl">
            S
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Sarah Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Legal Director, International Law Firm</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="flex text-yellow-400">
            <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          "The certified translations for our legal documents were delivered ahead of schedule and accepted by authorities in all jurisdictions. Impressive attention to detail."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a href="/testimonials" class="inline-block text-toast-600 font-medium hover:text-toast-700 transition-colors">
        Read More Success Stories →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>